#.vscode/

# Flutter/Dart/Pub related
**/doc/api/
**/ios/Flutter/.last_build_id
.dart_tool/
.flutter-plugins-dependencies
.pub-cache/
.pub/
# `build` is a symlink to an external SSD on the dev machine (disk-volume
# policy); a plain `/build/` only matches a real dir, so match the symlink too.
/build
/coverage/

# Symbolication related
app.*.symbols

# Obfuscation related
app.*.map.json

# Android Studio will place build artifacts here
/android/app/debug
/android/app/profile
/android/app/release
.vercel

# Vercel staging copy (build/web lives on the SSD via symlink)
/deploy_web/

# Local dev notes (never shared)
CLAUDE.md
test/fixtures/wild_local.*
